Package: open-agenda
Architecture: all
Version: 1.2.0
Maintainer: Open-Agenda Team <team@open-agenda.org>
Depends: python3, python3-tk
Description: Open-Agenda v1.2 - Firefox-Style Modern UI
 The best agenda in the world - Now with Firefox-style UI!
 .
 Features:
  - Firefox-style modern 2025 interface
  - Tab-based navigation (Calendar, Events, Dashboard, Settings)
  - Rounded corners and glass effects
  - Auto-save
  - Dark/Light theme toggle
  - Global search
  - Dashboard with statistics
  - Export to JSON/CSV
  - Import from JSON
  - Fully open source!
